# autoqcoder

[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/v2.0.0-production--ready-brightgreen.svg)](https://github.com/autoqcoder/autoqcoder)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
